<DialogueTree xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
                  xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Outer-Wilds-New-Horizons/new-horizons/main/NewHorizons/Schemas/dialogue_schema.xsd">
  <NameField>Leader of Exploration</NameField>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_0</Name>
    <EntryCondition>DEFAULT</EntryCondition>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>Greetings.</Page>
      <Page>You must be the one who gifted us the cockpit?</Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>Yep.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Init_00</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>Do you like it?</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Init_01</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>I think you have the wrong person.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Init_02</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_00</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>My clan and I express our gratitude.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <DialogueTarget>Init_1</DialogueTarget>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_01</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>The technology is suitable, yes. My clan and I thank you.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <DialogueTarget>Init_1</DialogueTarget>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_02</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>Have I brought the wrong person here?</Page>
      <Page>How strange... it is rare for me to make a mistake like this. Perhaps I should escort you out of the village while I search for the correct person.</Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>I was only joking.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Init_020</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>Sounds good.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Init_021</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_020</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>I see you are one for humor. Luckily, I too am fond of it.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <DialogueTarget>Init_1</DialogueTarget>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_021</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>You are fortunate in that I was not actually planning to do so.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <DialogueTarget>Init_1</DialogueTarget>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_1</Name>
    <EntryCondition>TALKED_TO_NOMAI_LEADER_B</EntryCondition>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>What would you request of me?</Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <CancelledPersistentCondition>GOT_NOMAI_SHARD_B</CancelledPersistentCondition>
        <Text>Will you help us open the Great Door?</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Door_0</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>What do you know about the fifth shard?</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Shard_0</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <RequiredPersistentCondition>TALKED_TO_NOMAI_LEADER_B</RequiredPersistentCondition>
        <Text>Just saying hi.</Text>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <RequiredPersistentCondition>GOT_NOMAI_SHARD_B</RequiredPersistentCondition>
        <CancelledPersistentCondition>TALKED_TO_NOMAI_LEADER_B</CancelledPersistentCondition>
        <CancelledPersistentCondition>LAST_CLAN_TO_AGREE</CancelledPersistentCondition>
        <Text>I'm glad you agreed to help us.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>End_00</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <RequiredPersistentCondition>LAST_CLAN_TO_AGREE</RequiredPersistentCondition>
        <RequiredPersistentCondition>GOT_NOMAI_SHARD_B</RequiredPersistentCondition>
        <CancelledPersistentCondition>TALKED_TO_NOMAI_LEADER_B</CancelledPersistentCondition>
        <Text>I'm glad you agreed to help us.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>End_01</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>
  
  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Init_2</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page></Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>What do you know about the fifth shard?</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>Shard_0</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <CancelledPersistentCondition>LAST_CLAN_TO_AGREE</CancelledPersistentCondition>
        <Text>I'm glad you agreed to help us.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>End_00</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <RequiredPersistentCondition>LAST_CLAN_TO_AGREE</RequiredPersistentCondition>
        <Text>I'm glad you agreed to help us.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>End_01</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Door_0</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>The task you ask of me is a great one. You ask me to give up what my clan has treasured for years to aid you.</Page>
      <Page>Nevertheless, you did aid our clan. It would seem like the logical course of action is to return that aid.</Page>
      <Page>There is also the undeniable fact that everyone is at least a little bit curious as to what lies behind the Great Door.</Page>
      <Page>As clan leader, I make the decision that the Followers of Exploration will help you in your mission and lend you our shard.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <RevealFacts>
      <FactID>BT_NOMAI_VILLAGE_B_AGREED</FactID>
    </RevealFacts>
    <SetPersistentCondition>GOT_NOMAI_SHARD_B</SetPersistentCondition>
    <DialogueTarget>Init_2</DialogueTarget>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Shard_0</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>The tale of the fifth shard is a common story among this clan. A scroll I read recently said this: "Travel to the north pole..."</Page>
      <Page>I hope this knowledge aids you on your journey.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <RevealFacts>
      <FactID>BT_FIFTH_SHARD_POS</FactID>
    </RevealFacts>
    <DialogueTarget>Init_1</DialogueTarget>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>End_00</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>The feeling is mutual. I hope convincing the other clans to join goes as smoothly as it did with mine, although I have my doubts.</Page>
      <Page>I will see you at the Great Door, my friend.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <SetPersistentCondition>TALKED_TO_NOMAI_LEADER_B</SetPersistentCondition>
    <SetPersistentCondition>NOMAI_VILLAGE_B_TO_DOOR</SetPersistentCondition>
  </DialogueNode>
  
  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>End_01</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>The feeling is mutual. I will see you at the Great Door, my friend.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <SetPersistentCondition>TALKED_TO_NOMAI_LEADER_B</SetPersistentCondition>
    <SetPersistentCondition>NOMAI_VILLAGE_B_TO_DOOR</SetPersistentCondition>
  </DialogueNode>
</DialogueTree>